              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer232507587685301320">This memoir made me miss teaching, and writing, and being a student, and Stuyvesant High School, and all of my wonderful and weird and thoughtful and mysterious and empathetic English teachers throughout the years. And now I&apos;ll greatly miss listening to Frank McCourt on my daily walks around my newly strange neighborhood. </span>
  <span id="freeText232507587685301320" style="display:none">This memoir made me miss teaching, and writing, and being a student, and Stuyvesant High School, and all of my wonderful and weird and thoughtful and mysterious and empathetic English teachers throughout the years. And now I'll greatly miss listening to Frank McCourt on my daily walks around my newly strange neighborhood. </span>
